'''2015年巴爾的摩暴動'''（{{lang-en|2015 Baltimore riots}}）發生於2015年4月，因[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]][[弗雷迪·格雷之死|弗雷迪·格雷之死]]（Freddie Gray）而产生。

==事件==
[[File:Maryland_National_Guard_(17285160576).jpg|缩略图]]
2015年4月25日，抗議群眾在{{link-en|巴爾的摩市中心|Downtown Baltimore}}集結，從{{link-en|巴爾的摩市政廳|Baltimore City Hall}}沿路遊行至{{link-en|內港 (巴爾的摩)|Inner Harbor|內港}}。在遊行活動進行到最後階段時，部分群眾變得更加暴力，他們毀損至少5臺警用車輛，並{{link-en|非法投擲石塊|Criminal rock throwing|向警察「投擲」石塊}}<ref name=Stolberg>{{cite news|last1=Stolberg|first1=Sheryl Grey|title=National Guard Activated in Baltimore as Police and Youths Clash After Funeral for Freddie Gray|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/28/us/a-call-for-peace-before-freddie-grays-funeral-in-baltimore.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&module=first-column-region&region=top-news&WT.nav=top-news&_r=0|accessdate=April 28, 2015|publisher=New York Times|date=August 27, 2015|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912060312/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/28/us/baltimore-freddie-gray.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。市長{{link-en|史蒂芬妮·羅林斯-布雷克|Stephanie Rawlings-Blake}}表示大部分群眾對警方多所尊重，但「有少部分煽動者干預了這場活動<ref name=":6" />。」市長也針對因抗議葛瑞的死而破壞公有財產的人表示，「我們也給那些希望破壞和平的人們，還以同樣的行動......<ref>[http://baltimore.cbslocal.com/2015/04/25/baltimore-mayor-gave-those-who-wished-to-destroy-space-to-do-that/ Baltimore Mayor: <nowiki>‘Gave Those Who Wished to Destroy Space to Do That’</nowiki>] {{Wayback|url=http://baltimore.cbslocal.com/2015/04/25/baltimore-mayor-gave-those-who-wished-to-destroy-space-to-do-that/ |date=20150428211352 }}, CBS News Baltimore, April 25, 2015</ref>。」當時警方逮捕至少34位民眾，衝突造成15名警察受傷<ref name=":8">{{Cite news|title = Baltimore police, protesters clash; 15 officers hurt|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/04/27/baltimore-credible-threat/26454875/|newspaper = USA Today|date = April 27, 2015|access-date = April 27, 2015|last = Bacon|first = John|archive-date = 2018-06-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180617193731/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/04/27/baltimore-credible-threat/26454875/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":6">{{Cite web|title = Freddie Gray death: 12 arrested during protests - CNN.com|url = http://www.cnn.com/2015/04/25/us/baltimore-freddie-gray-protest/index.html|website = CNN|accessdate = April 25, 2015|date = April 25, 2015|last = Marquez|first = Miguel|last2 = Almasy|first2 = Steve|archive-date = 2015-04-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150427220446/http://www.cnn.com/2015/04/25/us/baltimore-freddie-gray-protest/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>Wenger, Yvonne; Campbell, Colin. [http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/baltimore-city/bs-md-ci-protest-arrests-20150426-story.html City leader calls for peace after 35 arrested, 6 officers injured] {{Wayback|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/baltimore-city/bs-md-ci-protest-arrests-20150426-story.html |date=20150427211610 }}, ''[[Baltimore_Sun|Baltimore Sun]]'', April 26, 2015.</ref>。

